name: Who let the cats out?
description:
WELCOME ABOARD THE MOTHERSHIP CK-359!

You are now the MotherShip's new catkeeper! Isn't that excting?! (Well it should be, cuz you don't have a choice!)

You were brought to this world to take care of the cats, as if they are your family, and the Mother Ship, as if it is your home! So, welcome aboard! And most importantly, have fun!
